data.description: Discover this charming brick home with a full basement, offering potential for a third bedroom. The kitchen has been tastefully remodeled and features modern appliances. Enjoy moments of relaxation in the beautiful three-season room or the inviting living room, complete with a cozy fireplace. Both bedrooms are generously sized and provide ample storage space. Don't miss the opportunity to see this wonderful property in person; it's truly worth a visit!
